Package org.apache.nlpcraft.model.tools.embedded

Contains embedded probe controller. Embedded probe can be used to start a data probe in the same JVM process to save on REST network trips.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NCEmbeddedResult
    Result container for the embedded probe.

    Embedded probe controller.
